{"lemma":"عُصْمِ","slug":"عُصْمِ","root":"ع.ص.م","root_slug":"ع-ص-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ص-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُصْمِ","root":"عصم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29367","n29371","n29372","n29373"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to save"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to protect","examples":[{"text":"قَالَ سَآوِي إِلَى جَبَلٍ يَعْصِمُنِي مِنَ ٱلْمَاءِ ۚ قَالَ لَا عَاصِمَ ٱلْيَوْمَ مِنْ أَمْرِ ٱللَّهِ إِلَّا مَن رَحِمَ ۚ وَحَالَ بَيْنَهُمَا ٱلْمَوْجُ فَكَانَ مِنَ ٱلْمُغْرَقِينَ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29367","headword_ar":"عَصَمَ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSomN","text_ar":"عَصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaEa","text_ar":"مَنَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, prevented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hindered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as is generally the case,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protected"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:) this is [said to be] the primary signification: (TA: [but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapN","text_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, preserved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaY","text_ar":"وَقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it withheld"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amosaka","text_ar":"اَمْسَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") a thing. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamahu AlT~aEaAmu","text_ar":"عَصَمَهُ الطَّعَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamahu mina AljuwEi","text_ar":"عَصَمَهُ مِنَ الجُوعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The food prevented him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defended him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaEahu","text_ar":"مَنَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from being hungry."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamahu A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"عَصَمَهُ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb, TA,) aor. as above, (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapN","text_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) or this is a simple subst., (Msb,) and the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSomN","text_ar":"عَصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God defended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protected, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preserved him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Als~uwo'i","text_ar":"مِنَ السُّوْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Almakoruwhi","text_ar":"مِنَ المَكْرُوهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from what was disliked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hated"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamotuhu","text_ar":"عَصَمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protected, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preserved him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSama Alqirobapa","text_ar":"عَصَمَ القِرْبَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSomN","text_ar":"عَصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, to the water-skin, an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAm","text_ar":"عِصَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSamahaA","text_ar":"اَعْصَمَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISk, S, K, TA:) or the latter signifies, (TA,) or signifies also, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bound it with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAm","text_ar":"عِصَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) i. e. the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tie called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wikaA='","text_ar":"وِكَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is bound round its head to confine the contents"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSama A_ilayohi","text_ar":"عَصَمَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSama","text_ar":"عَصَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSomN","text_ar":"عَصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) signifies also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aikotasaba","text_ar":"اِكْتَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earned;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought means of subsistence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSama vaniy~atahu AlgubaAru","text_ar":"عَصَمَ ثَنِيَّتَهُ الغُبَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The dust stuck to his central incisor;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSaba","text_ar":"عَصَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSima","text_ar":"عَصِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamN","text_ar":"عَصَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * TA,) said of a gazelle, and of a mountain-goat, [and app. of a horse,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSamu","text_ar":"اَعْصَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Mgh","Msb","ISk","S"]},{"entry_id":"n29371","headword_ar":"عُصْمٌ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSumN","text_ar":"عُصُمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSiymN","text_ar":"عَصِيمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A relic,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a trace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything, (S, K,) such as tar [with which camels are smeared when mangy], (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiDaAb","text_ar":"خِضَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. hinnà ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hin~aA='","text_ar":"حِنَّا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":") and the like, with which one dyes, or tinges, the hair &c.], and the like: (S, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomN","text_ar":"عُصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also expl. as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a trace"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything such as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waros","text_ar":"وَرْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] or saffron or the like. (TA.) As says, I heard an Arab woman of the desert say to her follow-wife,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTiyniY EuSoma Hn~aAy^iki","text_ar":"اَعْطِينِى عُصْمَ حنَّايِكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Give me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what thou hast wiped off and cast away of thy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hin~aA='","text_ar":"حِنَّا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after thy dyeing of thy hands with it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomN","text_ar":"عُصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAmN","text_ar":"عِصَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n29372","headword_ar":"عِصْمٌ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomapN","text_ar":"عُصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n29373","headword_ar":"عُصُمٌ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomN","text_ar":"عُصْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAmN","text_ar":"عِصَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}